creator: Sakshi Media Group
descriptionHtml:
Sakshi.com, the online Telugu news portal from the Sakshi Media Group, brings you news as it breaks, from across the world. Catch events as they unfold in politics, business, crime, sports, science, entertainment and technology, covered by our network of seasoned and committed journalists.

Sakshi Android Mobile App a user-friendly mobile application gets you in-depth coverage and follow-up stories from a battery of veteran journalists - on local, national and international events; on moments that make and mar history; on a smart, cool site designed for people on the move and others across all ages and interests.
Download the Sakshi Mobile app to keep you updated on Latest Telugu News from Andhra Pradesh, Telangana and from across the world.

Sakshi Telugu Mobile App offers
Latest News from all corners of Andhra Pradesh, Telangana
Political news in Telugu from Andhra Pradesh, Telangana, India and across the world and from political parties including YSRCP, TDP, Jana Sena, Congress, BJP, TRS, etc
Telugu Movie News updates, Telugu Movie Reviews

Features:
• News by the minute: Breaking news, latest updates and videos across various categories including Politics, Entertainment, Movies, Sports, Business,
• Get all the local news from Andhra Pradesh and Telangana
• Breaking news notifications
• Watch Sakshi TV Live on the move
• Android app allows you to be a citizen journalist and share photos and videos from your device with the Sakshi app
• Voice Search in search page
• Text to speech in articles to listen news
